sect1.title: External Interfaces
sect1.para:
The external interface of DiagnosticTimers can be found in EA in the following location: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.UDS_Service_Chorus.SW Architecture.DiagnosticTimers.Integration context
A part of the external interfaces used by DiagnosticTimers is provided by the component "RTE Light" and includes generated interfaces which are based on the following SST files:
DiagnosticTimers_Sst.xlsx
